pg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025_vlure_weronikasikora_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025_vlure_weronikasikora_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/vlure">Vlure</a>宣布了新单曲“ Better Days”的回报 - 在下面查看。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：vlure：<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-radar/vlure-glasgow-interview-2021-3036767">格拉斯威格的朋克朋克乐队享受着汗水俱乐部的回归</a></strong></li></ul><p>欣快的歌曲是格拉斯哥乐队自2023年的“天堂send” EP以来的第一首。</p><p>在谈到单曲时，Vlure在新闻稿中说：“这是对朋友的颂歌，每天晚上，我们在握住生活的同时，牵着双手；每次我们的疯狂之后，每次我们拥抱并通过狗屎，我们沿途迷失的朋友，以及新的朋友，彼此之间的朋友。</p><p> “它遍布未来，并承认，尽管我们已经一起成长，无论生活有多艰难，我们将永远度过那些夜晚，而其他日子和夜晚都将来还没来。” </p><p><iframe title="Vlure-更好的日子（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/cWqMYXK-Jtc?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Written by brothers, programming and guitarist Conor and bassist Niall Goldie, &#39;Better Days&#39; has its “roots in the music the brothers grew up around, the icons of 90s dance music; <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/orbital">Orbital</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/underworld">Underworld</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/faithless">Faithless</a> . To say &#39;Better Days&#39; sits in this canon is no understatement; a spoken-word rave symphony that brings the genre firmly up to date, both musically and lyrically, incorporating the five piece&#39;s other影响力包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nitzer-ebb">Nitzer Ebb</a> ，PC音乐，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/front-242">前242</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-streets">街道</a>。”</p><p>该乐队目前正在为他们的首张专辑提供最后的效果，该专辑将于今年晚些时候为《国家》发行。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-leeds-2025-limp-bizkit-d-block-europe-heartworms-and-nell-mescal-lead-huge-line-up-additions-3842012">他们还将</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/CHAPPELL-ROAN">查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/TRAVIS-SCOTT">特拉维斯·斯科特（Travis Scott）</a>之类的人一起参加今年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reading-leeds-festival-2025">Reading＆Leeds</a>节日，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bring-me-the-horizon">带给我地平线</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/HOZIER">Hozier</a> 。今年的双节日版将在8月21日至24日之间举行。</p><p> <em>NME</em>在2022年回顾了他们的“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/vlure-euphoria-ep-radar-review-3137009">Euphoria</a> ” EP，授予了纪录的三颗星，并说“工业爆炸者都进入了格拉斯哥俱乐部俱乐部的黑暗之心”。</p><p>它补充说：“格拉斯哥乐队在舞池上度过了大流行的情感发行，他们的首次亮相EP使他们更近一步。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首先出现了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/vlure-return-with-blissed-out-banger-better-days-radar-3851446">带有幸福的Banger“ Beady Days”的帖子回报</a>。</p> ;
